Package hypervisorManager

In this package are located all classes to manage hypervisor processes to configure and execute images

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Context
    Responsible for changing the .vmx configuration file for executing a virtual machine fulfilling the user context
    Hypervisor
    Abstract class to be implemented by each hypervisor.
    HypervisorFactory
    Factory responsible for managing hypervisor classes and instances.
    VirtualBox
    Implementation of hypervisor abstract class to give support for VirtualBox hypervisor.
    VMwareAbstractHypervisor
    Implementation of hypervisor abstract class to give support for VMware hypervisor.
    VMwareWorkstation
    Implementation of hypervisor abstract class to give support for VMwareWorkstation hypervisor.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    HypervisorOperationException
    Exception to be used by hypervisors to notify hypervisor operations errors.

Package hypervisorManager Description

In this package are located all classes to manage hypervisor processes to configure and execute images
